main event: Multiple reports of unidentified flying objects sighted in Melbourne, Australia, during January 1954.
interesting points: Sighting occurred on January 5th, where a bright flying object was observed moving at approximately 700 mph, The object was reported to have dropped from the sky and remained stationary for a period of time, There was a description of a saucer-like object with green lights seen by the witnesses near a gravel quarry, Another sighting reported the object moved rapidly upwards at a steep angle, Witnesses described a metallic object with a diameter of 40-50 feet.
